  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个用户登录我们GitHub应用的完整流程。用户先打开前端界面，然后系统要引导他完成双重认证——AzureAD和企业GitHub都要验证。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User",
        "GhApp",
        "AzureAD",
        "GitHub"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，所以GhApp是前端应用，用户打开之后，GhApp主动发起认证请求对吗？然后AzureAD和GitHub这两个登录是并行还是串行的？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "GhApp",
        "AzureAD",
        "GitHub",
        "User"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是串行的，必须先过AzureAD拿到用户邮箱，再跳转GitHub。两个都确认之后，用户才能进入主界面操作任务。而且任务权限要根据用户在AzureAD里的群组来决定。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AzureAD",
        "GitHub",
        "GhApp",
        "user.email",
        "groups"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，我先画第一版：用户打开Frontend，GhApp请求认证，然后用户登录AzureAD，AzureAD把确认的邮箱返回给GhApp，接着用户再登录GitHub，GitHub确认后，用户就能基于他的访问权限完成任务了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User-GhApp",
        "GhApp-User",
        "User-AzureAD",
        "AzureAD-GhApp",
        "User-GitHub",
        "GitHub-GhApp"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "这里有个问题——AzureAD和GitHub返回给GhApp的消息应该用虚线箭头，因为是异步回调或者信息提供，不是同步调用。另外登录那两步要加上加号表示激活，显示这是阻塞性的用户操作。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AzureAD---GhApp",
        "GitHub---GhApp",
        "User-+AzureAD",
        "User-+GitHub"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已调整：User到AzureAD和User到GitHub都改成实线加号箭头，AzureAD返回user.email和GitHub的确认都用虚线箭头回传给GhApp。最后用户操作任务的步骤保持实线无加号。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User-+AzureAD",
        "User-+GitHub",
        "AzureAD---GhApp",
        "GitHub---GhApp",
        "User-GhApp"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，这样逻辑清晰了。最后一步的描述再精确一点——不是泛泛的'完成任务'，要强调是基于groups access control的权限过滤。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User-GhApp",
        "groups",
        "access to"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "最终确认：用户打开Frontend → GhApp请求认证 → 用户登录AzureAD（激活） → AzureAD确认并提供email → 用户登录GitHub（激活） → GitHub确认 → 用户基于可访问的群组权限完成任务。这样整个认证流程就完整了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User-GhApp",
        "GhApp-User",
        "User-+AzureAD",
        "AzureAD---GhApp",
        "User-+GitHub",
        "GitHub---GhApp",
        "groups",
        "access to"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    }
  ],
